Aspose::Email::Mapi::KnownPropertyList Class Referencefinal

The read-only Master Property List provides implementers with a single source of information about all the properties that are described by the specifications that comprise the Exchange Server Protocols documentation (MS-OXPROPS). Coincides MS-OXPROPS revision 16.2 from 7/31/2014 More...

Inherits System::Collections::Generic::IList< System::SharedPtr< Aspose::Email::Mapi::PropertyDescriptor > >.

class Aspose::Email::Mapi::PropertyDescriptor
 

Detailed Description

The read-only Master Property List provides implementers with a single source of information about all the properties that are described by the specifications that comprise the Exchange Server Protocols documentation (MS-OXPROPS). Coincides MS-OXPROPS revision 16.2 from 7/31/2014
